# Cloudflare Pages headers — Netlify-style format
# https://developers.cloudflare.com/pages/configuration/headers/

# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# AI agent discovery (RFC 8288 Link headers)
#
# Advertises agent-useful resources directly on the response, so an agent
# that issues a HEAD/GET on any HTML page learns about the discovery files
# without needing to parse the body.
#
# Relation types:
#   api-catalog    — RFC 9727: linkset of available APIs
#   service-doc    — RFC 8631: human/machine-readable service description
#   service-meta   — RFC 8631: machine-readable metadata about the service
#   sitemap        — IANA-registered: XML sitemap
#   describedby    — IANA-registered: schema/description resource
#
# A custom rel for agent-skills isn't IANA-registered yet, so we use an
# extension URI per RFC 8288 §2.1.2 (https://agentskills.io/rel/index).
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
/*
  Link: </.well-known/api-catalog>; rel="api-catalog"; type="application/linkset+json"
  Link: </llms.txt>; rel="service-doc"; type="text/plain"
  Link: </llms.txt>; rel="describedby"; type="text/plain"
  Link: </sitemap.xml>; rel="sitemap"; type="application/xml"
  Link: </.well-known/agent-skills/index.json>; rel="https://agentskills.io/rel/index"; type="application/json"

# Discovery documents — set explicit content types so agents see them as
# structured data instead of guessed text/plain.
/.well-known/api-catalog
  Content-Type: application/linkset+json; charset=utf-8
  Cache-Control: public, max-age=3600
  Access-Control-Allow-Origin: *

/.well-known/agent-skills/index.json
  Content-Type: application/json; charset=utf-8
  Cache-Control: public, max-age=3600
  Access-Control-Allow-Origin: *

# Keep llms.txt and llms-full.txt out of search engine indexes — they are
# meant for AI crawlers reading the file directly, not for SERP listings.
/llms.txt
  X-Robots-Tag: noindex
  Access-Control-Allow-Origin: *

/llms-full.txt
  X-Robots-Tag: noindex
  Access-Control-Allow-Origin: *
